      "rationale": "Relative error reported at 3 of 5 operating points; confidence bounds from Monte Carlo sampling are available but have not been formally linked to the comparison metric. Achieved level 2 against required level 4. The team notes that a sensitivity analysis to identify which input parameters drive the confidence bound width is planned but not yet performed."
