      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo sampling documented; dominant inputs identified through sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow rate and rotational speed assigned normal distributions based on pump tolerance specifications; Monte Carlo UQ completed with 500 samples. However, the dominant drivers of output variance have not been ranked — sensitivity analysis to identify which input parameters most influence hemolysis index uncertainty is explicitly deferred to a future assessment cycle. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
